tart; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;%3CmxGraphModel%3E%3Croot%3E%3CmxCell%20id%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3CmxCell%20id%3D%221%22%20parent%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3CmxCell%20id%3D%222%22%20parent%3D%221%22%20style%3D%22text%3Bhtml%3D1%3BwhiteSpace%3Dwrap%3BstrokeColor%3D%236F0000%3BfillColor%3D%23a20025%3Balign%3Dcenter%3BverticalAlign%3Dmiddle%3Brounded%3D0%3BfontColor%3D%23ffffff%3B%22%20value%3D%22%26lt%3Bb%26gt%3BEliminazione%20delle%20Gerarchie%20TIPO%202%26lt%3B%2Fb%26gt%3B%26amp%3Bnbsp%3B%26lt%3Bbr%26gt%3B%26lt%3Bbr%26gt%3B%26lt%3Bdiv%26gt%3B%26lt%3Bi%26gt%3BAccorpamento%20del%20genitore%20ai%20figli%26lt%3B%2Fi%26gt%3B%26lt%3B%2Fdiv%26gt%3B%26lt%3Bdiv%26gt%3B%26lt%3Bbr%26gt%3B%26lt%3B%2Fdiv%26gt%3B%26lt%3Bdiv%26gt%3B1)%20il%20PADRE%20non%20ha%20collegamenti%20(%C3%A8%20figlio%20a%20sua%20volta)%26lt%3B%2Fdiv%26gt%3B%26lt%3Bdiv%26gt%3B%26amp%3Bnbsp%3B2)%20tutti%20i%20collegamenti%20diversi%20tra%20loro%20sono%20sui%20FIGLI%26lt%3B%2Fdiv%26gt%3B%26lt%3Bdiv%26gt%3B3)%20Relazioni%20TOTALE%20DISGIUNTA%26lt%3B%2Fdiv%26gt%3B%26lt%3Bdiv%26gt%3B4)%20CUOCO%26amp%3Bnbsp%3B%20e%20COLLABORARE%20non%20avrebbero%20attributi%26lt%3B%2Fdiv%26gt%3B%22%20vertex%3D%221%22%3E%3CmxGeometry%20height%3D%22122.5%22%20width%3D%22298%22%20x%3D%22-1104%22%20y%3D%22695%22%20as%3D%22geometry%22%2F%3E%3C%2FmxCell%3E%3C%2Froot%3E%3C%2FmxGraphModel%3E&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1) Troppi attributi sia nel PADRE che ne FIGLIO&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;2) Attributi eterogeni&lt;br&gt;3) Accessi entità FIGLIO diversi da PADRE&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
